---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About AI Select" description="AI tools, reviewed honestly. By Selector Labs.">
  <div class="max-w-[42rem] mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-mono font-bold mb-8">About AI Select</h1>
    <div class="space-y-5 text-[#0F0F1B] leading-relaxed
      [&_h2]:text-xl [&_h2]:font-mono [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:mt-10 [&_h2]:mb-4
      [&_h2]:pb-2 [&_h2]:border-b [&_h2]:border-gray-100
      [&_a]:text-[#00B8A2] hover:[&_a]:underline
    ">
      <p class="text-lg text-[#6B7280]">We test AI tools. We write honestly. We sometimes get affiliate commission. We never let it dictate the verdict.</p>

      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>AI Select was built to answer one question: <em>"Which AI tool should I actually use?"</em> Every week we test web hosting platforms, VPNs, AI writing assistants, no-code builders, and automation tools. We compare them side by side, with real parameters, on real tasks.</p>

      <h2>How we make money</h2>
      <p>Some of the links on this site are affiliate links. If you click through and sign up, we may earn a commission — at no extra cost to you. We disclose this on every page. Our ratings and recommendations are never influenced by affiliate relationships. If a tool earns a low score, we publish the low score regardless of the commission structure.</p>

      <h2>Who runs this</h2>
      <p>AI Select is published by Selector Labs, an independent editorial project. We are not owned by, funded by, or affiliated with any of the tools we review.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p><a href="mailto:contact@aiselect.ai">contact@aiselect.ai</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
